## Sort [/movies/{page}{?sort}]
Movies can be sorted according to the following criteria:
- Trending
- Popularity
- Last added
- Top rated
- Year of publication

### Get movies by sort criteria [GET]
Returns an array of movies that correspond to the selected sort criteria.
  + Parameters
      + page (number, `1`) - The page of the content you want.
      + sort (string, `trending`) - Sort the list of content.
        + Values
              + `trending`
              + `popular`
              + `released`
              + `rating`
              + `year`

  + Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            sharix-api-authorization:[access_token]
            sharix-api-version: 1

  + Response 200 (application/json; charset=utf-8)

      + Body

            [{"_id":"UniqueString1","imdb_id":"UniqueString1","title":"String","year":0,"slug":"String","synopsis":"String","runtime":0,"rating":{"percentage":0,"watching":0,"votes":0},"images":{"banner":"String","fanart":"String","poster":"String"},"genres":["String"],"type":"String","language":"String","released":0,"trailer":"String","certification":"String","clusters":{"en":{"1080p":{"provider":"String","filesize":"String","size":0,"peer":0,"seed":0,"url":"String"},"720p":{"provider":"String","filesize":"String","size":0,"peer":0,"seed":0,"url":"String"}}}}]

      + Attributes (array[Movie])

